sentence.text: Evidence for association with endometriosis was also found for the AC genotype of the rs10859871 of cell-cell adhesion.

In this study, we investigated whether single nucleotide polymorphisms (SNPs) rs7521902, rs10859871 and rs11031006, mapping to negative regulation of gene expression, VEZT and FSHB genetic loci, respectively, are associated with risk for endometriosis in a Greek population.
